summaries.short: The Gebaras are imprisoned. Rafael and Claudio assume a policeman disappeared with the pen drive.
summaries.full: The Gebaras are imprisoned. Rafael and Claudio assume a policeman disappeared with the pen drive. With the help of his friend, Judge Norberto Bueno, and Ana Cristina’s father, Rafael tries to get Claudio out of jail. Brown asks Gloria to give his car keys to officer Clemente. She, on the other hand, will have to keep something she will receive safe.

summaries.short: Claudio and Nilo leave the prison. Gloria suggests to Brown that he should confess his treason to his brothers.
summaries.full: Claudio and Nilo leave the prison. Gloria suggests to Brown that he should confess his treason to his brothers. He refuses and tries to persuade her to return with him. Meanwhile, Comodoro learns that Brown received aid from the police in the operation to take the pen drive away. Rosana makes two shocking revelations to Nilo that lead to trouble.

summaries.short: The Gebaras are getting ready to celebrate Christmas. A romance begins between Gloria and Claudio.
summaries.full: The Gebaras are getting ready to celebrate Christmas. A romance begins between Gloria and Claudio. Comodoro, becoming impatient, activates his contacts with the police and sets his revenge on foot. Claudio, Nilo, and Brown are detained and taken to prison for crimes of tax evasion and gearing a criminal gang.

summaries.short: Season Two Finale. Gloria talks Brown into telling the truth to his brothers, since they may be his only hope against Comodoro.
summaries.full: Season Two Finale. Gloria talks Brown into telling the truth to his brothers since they are the only ones who can protect him from Comodoro. By the end, only Nilo can avenge the family. Without anything to lose, he decides to go to the old vampire's house to settle accounts.

summaries.short: 'Rios Kings.' Rafael offers some advice to Nilo; Cris invites his friends to the shed where things take an unexpected turn.
summaries.full: 'Rios Kings.' Thinking that the slot business is substituting the illegal bets in the streets of Rio, Rafael tries to convince Nilo to eliminate a large number of bet points. Meanwhile, Claudio's son Cris invites a group of friends to play slots at the shed, but things take an unexpected turn. Brown prepares to launch a new stage in the Samba School.

summaries.short: 'Paternal Heritage.' Claudio resorts to all means to locate the missing Deo, his right-hand man in slot-chip smuggling.
summaries.full: 'Paternal Heritage.' Claudio resorts to all means to find out Deo's whereabouts. The torture applied on Reinaldo, Síio's employee, is effective; Deo is located and Reinaldo's destiny is forged. Claudio decides to ask his brothers for help and fulfills the promise made to his widow.
